The below code is using the Local network transmission to transmit the command and stablis the connection between the application and ESP module
The below code must be uploaded to the NodeMCU ESP 8266.
The Softwae used to upload the code is ARDUINO IDE
The fllowing libraries must be installed before compiling the code:
  ESP8266WiFi
  ESP8266WebServer
  ESP8266HTTPClient
Update the IP of ESP address in the API in the application 
